Music::Tag::Lyrics version 0.26
===============================

Plugin module for Music::Tag to grab lyrics from the web.

Note:  As of version 0.28, Music-Tag is distributed as seperate packages.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Music::Tag
   Cache::Cache
   File::Spec
   LWP
   URI::Escape
   URI::WithBase
   XML::Simple

The version info in the Makefile is based on what I use.  You can get 
away with older versions in many cases. 

